# SmartPredict ML Inference Platform

A Full-Stack, Cloud-Deployed ML Inference Platform with Secure Authentication & Interactive Predictions

## Overview

This project is a cloud-based ML inference platform that allows users to:

- Log in securely with JWT-based authentication
- Upload datasets or input numeric features for predictions
- Perform predictions using integrated ML models
- View results with interactive charts and graphs
- Test APIs directly via Swagger UI
- Deploy easily with Docker and CI/CD pipelines


