## Features

- **User Authentication & Authorization**: Secure login with JWT tokens  
- **ML Model Integration**: Extensible architecture to add multiple ML models  
- **Interactive Predictions**: Visualized results with charts and graphs  
- **API Documentation**: Professional Swagger UI documentation for backend endpoints  
- **Dockerized Backend & Frontend**: Simplifies deployment and scalability  
- **CI/CD Ready**: Automated GitHub Actions pipeline for testing and deployment  
- **Cloud Ready**: Designed for AWS/GCP deployment with secure storage & networking  

---

## Installation & Run Locally

### Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Jasleen-Kaur655/SmartPredict-ML-Inference-Platform.git
cd SmartPredict-ML-Inference-Platform

## Backend setup

cd backend
python -m venv venv

# Linux/macOS
source venv/bin/activate

# Windows
venv\Scripts\activate

pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn main:app --reload


## Frontend setup

cd frontend
npm install
npm start


## Open your browser at http://localhost:3000
